Question: The right image shows one panda posed on its back with at least one front paw raised and mouth open.

Reference Answer: False

Original program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='How many pandas are in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the panda posed on its back?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is at least one front paw raised?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the mouth open?')
ANSWER4=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} == 1 and {ANSWER1} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER3}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER4)
```
